content: liamzebedee: Opened two PRs this month: #454 to fix tweet reply behavior and #448 to improve error handling for character loading failures. Created two issues (#492 and #695) related to running the application using Bun.sh, both of which were subsequently closed. Made a small code contribution with 1 commit modifying a single file (+1/-0 lines), showing sporadic activity with participation on only one day this month.
